         <abstract id="aspace_b6baf26eec7f78bad9cf8f38d596512f">Reports of agents of the East India Company in Mahi Kantha in Gujarat (western India) and dispatches from East India officials in Bombay sent to London. The reports provide a history of the Mahi Kantha before 1821 and describe political events there through 1839. The documents are all copies.</abstract>
